== Note ==
#{{note|EMD}} ''Entitats municipals descentralitzades'' are governed by the ''Llei Municipal i de R<U+00E8>gim Local de Catalunya'' (8/1987 de 15 d'abril de 1987). They correspond to ''entidades locales menores'' in the rest of Spain (known as ''entitats locals menors'' in the [[Valencian Community]] and the [[Balearic Islands]]).

